'''Krischka Stoffels''', ni umukinnyi wa firime wo muri [[Namibiya]] <ref>https://www.stage32.com/profile/374788/about</ref>. Krischka yakoze firime nyinshi zizwi cyane harimo ''Gesie muri die glas'' na ''Tjiraa'' <ref>https://frankensaurus.com/Krischka_Stoffels</ref>.  Usibye icyerekezo, ni na producer, umwanditsi, cinematografi akaba n'umwanditsi.<ref>https://www.africavenir.org/nc/news-details/article/women-in-namibian-film-three-short-films-by-female-directors-from-namibia-14-may-18h30-fnc.html</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
She was born in Windhoek, Namibia<ref>https://confidentenamibia.com/tributes-pour-in-for-film-icon-ndjavera/</ref>.

== Career ==
Mu mwaka wa 2010, yakoze filimi ngufi, ''Gesie muri die glas'', yatsindiye igihembo kidasanzwe cyo kuvuga muri [[Namibiya|Namibian]] Film and Theatre Awards<ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/202106220706.html</ref>.  ''Nitsinzi'', yakoze Tjiraa ye filimi ya kabiri ngufi. Iyi filime ikurikira Vezuva, umukobwa ukiri muto wa Ovaherero wagarutse avuye kwiga mu mahanga, mu [[Budage]], gusa yaje kubona ko mubyara we washatse yitabye Imana, kandi ko nk'uko bisanzwe, biteganijwe ko azashyingira umupfakazi wa mubyara we.<ref>https://www.thefreelibrary.com/BEST+NAMIBIAN+FILM+AND+THEATRE+PRODUCTIONS+AWARDED.-a0655229940</ref>  Iyi filime yatewe inkunga na komisiyo ishinzwe amafilime ya [[Namibiya]] kandi yatoranijwe kugira ngo yerekanwe mu birori mpuzamahanga  bya filime, harimo iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya filime rya Afurika Diaspora<ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/200905111114.html</ref> .<ref>https://www.screenafrica.com/2010/10/27/film/namibian-film-awards/</ref> 

